oneYearLater.setFullYear(oneYearLater.getFullYear() + 1) return oneYearLater.toISOString().split('T')[0] } let [userRegDetails, setUserRegDetails] = useState({ s_entity_id: '', s_entity_id_and_name: setShowConfirmPassword(!showConfirmPassword) } let handleNameChange = (e, s_entity_id1) => { let { name, value } = e.target if (name === 's_entity_id_and_name') { setUserRegDetails(prevData => ({ ...prevData, s_entity_id_and_name: value, s_entity_id: s_entity_id1 })) } } let [entityNames, setEntityNames] = useState({ data: [] }) useEffect(() => { fetch(`${ubuntuIP}/api/v0/getAllEntityNameList`) .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setEntityNames({ data }) }) .catch(error => { console.error('Error: ', error) }) }, []) let [timezone, setTimezone] = useState({ data: [] }) useEffect(() => { fetch(`${ubuntuIP}/api/v0/timezones`) .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { setTimezone({ data }) }) .catch(error => { console.error('Error: ', error) }) }, []) let [passwordMatch, setPasswordMatch] = useState(true) let resetForm = () => { setUserRegDetails(initialState) } let refreshPage = () => { window.location.reload() } let handleChange = e => { let { name, value, type, checked } = e.target if (name === 's_trans_cnf_pass') { let match = value === userRegDetails.s_trans_pass setPasswordMatch(match) } setUserRegDetails(prevData => ({ ...prevData, [name]: type === 'checkbox' ? checked : value })) } let handleSubmit = e => { e.preventDefault() fetch(`${ubuntuIP}/api/v0/setUserInfo`, { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify(userRegDetails) }) .then(response => response.json()) .then(data => { console.log('Success in User Creation Form:', data) alert('User created successfully!') }) .catch(error => { console.error('Error:', error) alert('Error!
